data.description: Ready in April - The Oakmont floor plan by Pulte Homes in Sunterra offers a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home at 1,795 sq.ft. Modern kitchen, ample living spaces, and serene owner's suite with bay windows. The versatile layout accommodates family gatherings and relaxation. Many features include modern cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, Vinyl flooring, a sprinkler system, and MUCH MORE. Zoned to Katy ISD. Sunterra Community features a 3.5-acre Crystal Blue Lagoon with white sand beaches, palm trees, cabanas, watercraft rentals of kayaks, paddleboards, etc. Clubhouse, event center, swim-up beach bar, swimming pool, and splash pad – resort-style living at its finest!
